<i>adjective</i>: 부단하다 [부단하다], 면면하다 [면면하다], 끊임없다 [끄니멉따] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>부단하다 [부단하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. continual; ceaseless; constant</dd><br>
<dd>꾸준하게 이어져 끊임이 없다.</dd><br>
<dd>Continuing without a pause.</dd><br>
<dd>2. indecisive</dd><br>
<dd>결단력이 없다.</dd><br>
<dd>Lacking determination.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>면면하다 [면면하다]</dt><br>
<dd>continuous; ceaseless; endless</dd><br>
<dd>끊어지지 않고 죽 이어져 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being connected all the way through without a break.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>끊임없다 [끄니멉따]</dt><br>
<dd>incessant; unceasing; ceaseless</dd><br>
<dd>계속하거나 이어져 있던 것이 끊이지 아니하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Something that has been continued or connected being not interrupted.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>